TESTCASES for the WapIT Open Source SMS Gateway
by gw@wapit.com.

xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

NOTE: This file is ONLY for old SMS Gateway, not for the Kannel!
(SMS and WAP Gateway)

xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

This file lists each step of the test cases that a release candidate
of the gateway must pass before a new release can be made. Any problems
must be fixed or documented in the release notes.


1. Unpack the distribution .tar.gz.

2. Compile the gateway. There must not be any error messages, or worrisome
warning messages (most warning messages can be fixed in the next release).

3. Run a trivial test case:

	terminal 1: ./fakesmsc 10000 1 1 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 2: ./smsgateway tests/trivial.conf

4. Run a heavier test case:

	terminal 1: ./fakesmsc 10000 1 100 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 2: ./smsgateway tests/trivial.conf

5. Run an even more heavier test case:

	terminal 1: ./fakesmsc 10000 0.01 1000 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 2: ./smsgateway tests/trivial.conf

6. Test multiple SMS centers:

	terminal 1: ./fakesmsc 10000 0.01 1000 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 2: ./fakesmsc 10001 0.01 1000 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 3: ./fakesmsc 10002 0.01 1000 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 4: ./fakesmsc 10003 0.01 1000 '123 456 nop'
	terminal 5: ./smsgateway tests/several.conf

